# Supabase Standards

This project uses Supabase directly from the Angular frontend.

There is no custom backend for the MVP.

## General Rules

- Keep all Supabase calls inside Angular services.
- Do not call Supabase directly from components.
- Always filter data by the authenticated user.
- Use Row Level Security in Supabase.
- Do not expose secret keys in the frontend.
- Only use the public anon key in the Angular app.

## Environment

Supabase config should come from environment files:

```ts
export const environment = {
  production: false,
  supabaseUrl: '',
  supabaseAnonKey: '',
};